Text:
@Maroonylife
TPB has been moving to eliminate .torrent files for some time now. The new default is Magnet files (hance the little magnet icon). I would be lying if I said I could tell you the functional difference when using them on a desktop (I've noticed no difference from mine); as a guy on the go, however, I suffer from no longer being able to use other people's computers (school library, your mom's house, etc.) to DL the .torrent and upload it to my Dropbox/Torrents folder, which my BT program auto-loads/deletes from.
If anybody has a suggestion for a workaround (not involving RDC) that would be great.
